<i>adjective</i>: 반듯하다 [반드타다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt>반듯하다 [반드타다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. straight</dd><br>
<dd>비뚤어지거나 굽거나 흐트러지지 않고 바르다.</dd><br>
<dd>Straight, not bent, tilted, or crooked.</dd><br>
<dd>2. clean-cut; handsome</dd><br>
<dd>생김새가 훤하고 말끔하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Good-looking and neat.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>